dimmed thoughtfully. Finally he raised his optics to once again look
at NIGHTSHIFT, and he began to speak.

&quot;When the Maximals once against started coming back to Earth after the
first Beast Wars, the watchers . . . &quot; There was a pause before he
continued, &quot; . .  I mean WE watchers we sent back by the council to
keep an optic on things. At first we were to chronicle the unfolding
events here on Earth, but never to interfere. To observe how the
humans and other life forms progressed and catalog all we found and
send word back to Cybertron.&quot;

LORD ELDER shook his head, &quot;But then the Mephilis crash landed setting
untold number of criminals free on Earth and it changed our entire
mission.&quot;

